{"tid":1803760,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[財經界魔鬼]善意提醒趨吉避凶","createTime":"2019-12-30T12:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T22:11:34.000Z","uid":325838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ee569fc36b733dde6e7f016547da33e726c23527","tid":1803760,"uid":325838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"假如被魔鬼附身的人接觸過一些物品, 這些物品就具有魔性, 魔鬼就可以隨時在這些物品中隨意穿梭(類似量子糾纏原理), 並透過這些物件對你附身, 令你出現種種健康問題, 所以被附魔的人觸碰過的物件, 包括鍵盤和滑鼠, 一定要徹底消毒清潔, 將表面的皮膚粒子清走。<br />\n<br />\n以上就是降頭師傅托我帶給耀才員工的訊息, 救得一個得一個。"},{"pid":"b12a8b88a638a34fc031af8a332edcf395f95a6b","tid":1803760,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=4c02b2f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=17f4e2b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要33000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetitio